{"tid":844991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【與魔同贏】有前科！曼9先苦後甜","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T14:03:07.000Z","uid":8619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62090cbc16ecccd00b8225580b31d7b29b461a90","tid":844991,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"真獌9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家講曼聯今季將會奇迹反超前捧英超冠軍，似乎有啲天方夜譚，但並非夢話，因為紅魔鬼同「9」有緣。 <br />\n<br />\n英超成立之後，曼聯於1998/99年球季成為英超、英足盃、歐聯「三冠王」。2008/09年球季亦成為英超及英聯盃雙料冠軍。 <br />\n<br />\n最值得留意係曼聯上述兩季都係先苦後甜，1998/99年球季曼聯頭3場英超都贏唔到，當年歐聯6場分組賽亦只有2勝。 <br />\n<br />\n至於2008/09年球季曼聯同樣開局唔順，頭4場聯賽只有1勝，歐聯分組賽同樣贏得2場，但最後都殺入決賽。 <br />\n<br />\n又相隔10年，今季2018/19年球季，曼聯隨時又來個大逆轉。 <br />\n<br />\n東網體育FB同你追實體壇每個精彩時刻！ <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ecTF2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ecTF2A&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=50d2f531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ecTF2A</a>　 <br />\n<br />\nFollow東網體育IG一齊撐本地運動員！ <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EYxoRh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EYxoRh&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=74ad8bf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2EYxoRh</a>　"},{"pid":"0127f05d9a9e891f2b0bef55f83ecfb839f60c99","tid":844991,"uid":18385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"剩下全勝可以了"},{"pid":"40a4d638b687ecf0ee30d6950b0a3656f5ce271d","tid":844991,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"呢個飛機打唔落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78cb63c600c4920a876dbcfc2453c7bfe0d0979","tid":844991,"uid":25688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score